Section Headings
================

Section headings are lines beginning with '#' (number sign).  There are
five levels of section headings, with additional '#' characters demoting
the outline level of a heading.

     # Top-Level Heading

     ## Sub-Heading

     ### Sub-Sub-Heading

   *Note Outlining::.


